Info
--------------------

A Basic Example to demonstrate Spring-Data 

Steps Summary
1) Add Gradle Dependency
    compile("org.springframework.boot:spring-boot-starter-data-jpa")
    
2) Design PoJo Class
	Annotate with @Entity
	and ID for Primary Keys
	
3) Design Custom Interface for adding custom methods apart from basic CRUD
	i.e
	interface customRepo ... extends CrudRepository<Customer, Long>
		add methods for custom Queries
	 
4) To run using Spring Boot
	define Application class with main and annotated with 
	@SpringBootApplication
	
	and consume your CustomRepository 
	with SpringData generating all the boilerPlate code for you.
	

 